SUMMARY:Fair Oaks Recreation Complex Grand-Opening
LOCATION:3400 East Louisiana Avenue Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:The time has finally come for the Grand Opening of the Fair Oa
 ks Recreation Complex! We want to see you\, your family and friends\, Satu
 rday\, May 9\, from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. at Fair Oaks Recreation Complex\, 34
 00 East Louisiana Avenue. Come celebrate this momentous occasion with Mayo
 r Jane Castor and her team along with Tampa City Council. You will get the
  opportunity to explore all this state-of-the-art park has to offer from t
 he splash pad to the athletic field. KNOW BEFORE YOU GO: It is going to be
  a warm day We have beautifully shaded sitting areas around the complex\, 
 however if youd like to freely sit where youd like\, please bring a lawn c
 hair. Other Items to consider bringing Extra Water Blanket Handheld fan Um
 brella Sunscreen Comfortable shoes Bug Spray Hat \n\nPermalink: https://ww
 w.tampa.gov/node/189766
