SUMMARY:Dog Mom039\\\;s Day - Bay Paws Ybor
LOCATION:1212 N 34th Street Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Calling All DOG MOMS Join us at Bay Paws Pet Resort Ybor for D
 og Moms Day\, an event designed to pamper you and your furry best friend. 
 WHATS HAPPENING: For Mom: Sip on complimentary mimosas while enjoying deli
 cious appetizers and sweet treats. For the Kids (Pups!): A DIY craft stati
 on where your pup (with a little human help) can make Mom a custom gift. E
 xplore: Take a tour of our facility and see what the Bay Paws life is all 
 about! EXCLUSIVE EVENT PACKAGE SAVINGS:Take advantage of our best rates of
  the season! Not only do these save you money\, but they also give you the
  best chance to win the Grand Prize. 5-Day Promo 20 OFF  1 Free Day 180 En
 richment 136 Daycare10-Day Promo 20 OFF  2 Free Days: 344 Enrichment 272 D
 aycare THE ULTIMATE PAMPERING GIVEAWAY:Win a prize package valued at nearl
 y 500\, including a Michael Kors Handbag and a 200 Massage Envy Gift Card!
  FREE and Open to the COMMUNITY! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node
 /189556
