SUMMARY:BAPS Charities WalkRun 2026
LOCATION:4810 N Himes Ave Tampa \, FL 33614 United States
DESCRIPTION:Driven by our motto\, The Spirit of Service\, the BAPS Chariti
 es WalkRun is an annual event that has raised vital funds for over 20 year
 s for: BAPS Charities: Funding our five key areas: Health Awareness\, Educ
 ational Services\, Humanitarian Relief\, Environmental Protection\, and Co
