SUMMARY:Remix: Mysteries of the Nile
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Remix is a series of make-and-take art workshops for adults in
 spired by the Museums current exhibitions with a new project every month. 
 This months project will be inspired by our upcoming Mysterious of the Nil
 e: Ancient Egypt exhibition\, focusing on printmaking with an Egyptian foc
 us. Workshops are designed to be enjoyed by participants of any skill leve
 l\, and all materials are provided. Ages 18  Beginner Level \n\nPermalink:
  https://www.tampa.gov/node/189166
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189166
