SUMMARY:Blind Date with a Book
LOCATION:W Kennedy Blvd &amp\; W Grand Central Ave Tampa \, FL 33606 Unite
 d States
DESCRIPTION:Its a match! Swipe right on a good read and start a new chapte
 r together during Blind Date with a Book. Each novel has page-turner poten
 tial but is wrapped to hide the cover  its bound to be good! Join us to un
 wrap a new favorite and experience love at first page. This event happens 
 four times a year\, so its the perfect opportunity to stay booked and busy
 ! WHEN: February 9\, August 10  4:30-7:30pm WHERE: Snow Park The Tampa Dow
 ntown Partnership is partnering with Oxford Exchange and TeBella Tea Compa
 ny on this program. In addition\, huge thank you to our sponsordonor the H
 illsborough Public Library (Seminole Heights Location) for their help with
  this program. El amor est en el aire! Comienza tu nueva historia de amor 
 con nuestra Cita a Ciegas Con Un Libro. Cada obra viene envuelta y ocultan
 do su portada. La idea es que el libro que escojas sea una sorpresa! Acomp
 anos para descubrir tu nueva aventura (y quin sabe? tal vez un amor a prim
 era pgina). El evento es cuatro veces al ao\, as que es la oportunidad per
 fecta para mantenerte ocupado! CUANDO: 9 de febrero\, 10 de agosto  4:30-7
 :30pm DONDE: Parque Snow \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/179436
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/179436
END:VEVENT
